  "note": [
    {
      "text": "Second consecutive first-trimester pregnancy loss. Embryonic demise confirmed by absent growth and absent cardiac activity on serial transvaginal ultrasounds (6-week and 7-week scans). CRL consistent with growth arrest at approximately 6 weeks 2 days. Patient elected expectant management; miscarriage completed spontaneously over approximately 10 days. Beta-hCG confirmed complete resolution (<5 mIU/mL) on 2024-11-04."
    }
